<ArticleLayout
  title="Drying Cannabis — Getting It Right in Hawaii's Humidity"
  description="Drying is where a lot of good harvests go wrong. Too fast and you lose terpenes. Too slow in Hawaii's humidity and you get mold. Here's the process and how to manage it in a tropical climate."
  silo="Equipment & Tools"
